output_list.impact: Integer overflow in setBounty function allows the owner to set the total bounty amount to any value.
Integer overflow in setSpareOwner function allows the owner to set the spare owner address to any value.
Integer overflow in switchBounty function allows the owner to switch the bounty status to any value.
Integer overflow in burnRemainingBounty function allows the owner to burn the remaining bounty amount to any value.
Integer overflow in withdrawBounty function allows the owner to withdraw the bounty amount to any value.
Integer overflow in unfreezeBounty function allows the owner to unfreeze the bounty status to any value.
Integer overflow in setOwner function allows the owner to set the new owner address to any value.
